author: Written by: Kelly Weston, Digital Content Producer
title: Rape suspect out of Jeff Parish caught in St. John
text:
JEFFERSON PARISH, LA (WVUE) - The Jefferson Parish Sheriff's Office says a rape suspect sought earlier in the week has been caught.
Gerson Rodriguez, 28, was apprehended by the St. John Parish Sheriff's Office Wednesday evening.
Rodriguez will be booked in St. John Parish as a fugitive from Jefferson Parish. Upon his release he will be taken to the Jefferson Parish Correctional Center and booked with first-degree rape.
